	<td class="alt1" id="td_post_1226336">
	
		
		<!-- message -->
		<div id="post_message_1226336">
                  
                  It is often stated that the Barrier spells are analogous to forms or stances.  In order to make it easier to switch among them (noting of course the predominance of Fire Barrier) as a patch did with the psionicist forms?  Previously the psionicst forms were located on the hot key bars like most abilities however this was eventually altered.  Do you think that a similar thing would be a good idea with the Barrier lines to make it easier to switch among them and emphasis their difference from typical buffs?  The location in this situation would be to the left of the finishers where several classes have stances/forms located.
                  
		</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
	</td>
